# Safety net. Runtime state (auth.json, history.jsonl, log/, sessions/)
# should never land here: Codex reads and writes runtime state under
# ~/.codex (bind-mounted from /srv/devhome/.codex), not in this repo dir.
# This repo tracks only shared Codex config and subagent definitions.
# If any runtime-state file nevertheless appears here, this .gitignore keeps
# it out of commits — treat its presence as a bug and investigate why Codex
# wrote here instead of ~/.codex.
auth.json
auth.*.json
history.jsonl
log/
sessions/
themes/
cache/
tmp/
state/
